![Oneshot.jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1618452483460-LZOH2IES5P4D1EQ8AZYF/Oneshot.jpg)

**Megan Huang** is going to be the talk of the comic book world very soon, but until then she was graceful enough to talk to us about her pathway into comics, whether pineapple belongs on pizza, and her journey to creating her OWN comic book published by Dark Horse Comics, **Rangers of The Divide**! Join us as we talk to one of the brightest new talents to come to comic books and comic book media! **  
  
